        <p class="lede-p"><strong>Clearscope is the most accurate content grader on the market.</strong> It is also priced for enterprise content teams, not solo bloggers — $189/mo gets you 10 reports, $399/mo gets you 50. After 30 days running side-by-side grades against Surfer and Frase on 22 articles, plus tracking 90-day SERP outcomes, here is the honest verdict and the real total monthly cost of running SEO content with Clearscope.</p>

