          <p>This review was written and published by theStacc, a competing product. We have a commercial interest as an alternative. Every feature claim and price was verified against Clearscope's public pricing page as of Q2 2026. Where we are biased, we say so.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="callout callout-tldr">
