          <p>Every Clearscope customer we interviewed underestimated this by <strong>15–20×</strong>. They saw $189/mo and budgeted $189/mo. They actually spend $4,000–$6,500/mo to turn Clearscope grades into published, ranking articles. The grade is honest about what it does — the gap is in how teams calculate their <em>real</em> SEO budget.</p>
