        <h2 id="performance">Performance — Clearscope grade vs actual rankings</h2>
        <p>We graded 22 articles across 3 client sites and tracked 90-day SERP outcomes. Articles were grouped by final Clearscope grade (A+, A, B, C). All articles had similar word counts, internal linking, and publication conditions.</p>

        <div class="stat-grid">
          <div class="stat-cell"><div class="stat-num">73%</div><div class="stat-lbl">A+ articles ranked top 20 in 60 days</div></div>
          <div class="stat-cell"><div class="stat-num">55%</div><div class="stat-lbl">A articles ranked top 20 in 60 days</div></div>
